name: SearchRank
tag_list: seo, sem, smm, smo, link-building, ppc
overview:
Founded in 1997, SearchRank is an original search and social media marketing company that is based in Phoenix, Arizona. They provide strategic search engine marketing and social media marketing services for Fortune 500 companies, international businesses, small businesses and entrepreneurs from just about every type of industry.

SearchRank’s primary goal is to build long-lasting business relationships by providing a superior service over the competition. They will work diligently to obtain top visibility and increase return on investment for your business without resorting to unethical marketing techniques that some SEOs and SEMs use today.

SearchRank offers customized solutions for organic search engine optimization (SEO), link popularity building, online reputation management, pay for click (PPC) management and social media marketing.

They can also offer web site design/development, hosting and SEO consulting services for those who want to manage their own search engine marketing campaigns but need some extra guidance and hand holding.
